{"search_data": "BiharBihar Mukhymantri Vaas Sthal Kray Sahayata Yojana \u2013 Rs. 60,000 to Purchase Land for House Bihar Mukhymantri Vaas Sthal Kray Sahayata Yojana (MVSKSY) launched for SC / ST / OBC people to provide assistance of Rs. 60,000 to purchase land for own houses, this scheme will enable people to avail assistance of Rs. 1.2 lakh for construction of new houses under Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana Gramin (PMAY-G) housing schemeBihar Mukhymantri Vaas Sthal Kray Sahayata Yojana (MVSKSY)Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana Gramin (PMAY-G) is providing financial assistance of Rs. 1,20,000 to the rural people for construction of new homes. But some people belonging to SC / ST / OBC category does not have the land to build their own homes. So they are deprived of availing the benefits of PMAY-G housing scheme. Govt. has prepared the complete list of such people from the Socio-Economic Caste Census (SECC) 2011 data.Now the state govt. will provide an assistance of Rs. 60,000 to such SC / ST / OBC category people in order to enable them to purchase their own land. This would make them eligible to avail the benefits of Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana Gramin and realize their dream of having their own house. Govt. will not charge any registration fees on the purchase of these lands.Rural development department is going to provide assistance to around 22,000 people in the next 5 months under Mukhymantri Vaas Sthal Kray Sahayata Yojana.\u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0938\u091a\u093f\u0935\u093e\u0932\u092f \u0938\u094d\u0925\u093f\u0924 \u2018\u0938\u0902\u0935\u093e\u0926\u2019 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u2018\u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0935\u093e\u0938 \u0938\u094d\u0925\u0932 \u0915\u094d\u0930\u092f \u0938\u0939\u093e\u092f\u0924\u093e \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e\u2019 \u090f\u0935\u0902 \u2018\u092e\u0941\u0916\u094d\u092f\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0917\u094d\u0930\u093e\u092e\u0940\u0923 \u09